      • extractLargeChunks

        public RegionFile extractLargeChunks(ChunkPos pos)
                              throws java.io.IOException
        In 1.14, Forge added support for large chunks by allowing it to overflow the 255 section limit. Deferring the section size to the 'length' header in front of the chunk data. In 1.15, Mojang solved this issue by adding an external '.mcc' file for large chunks. Here, we attempt to detect and extract these large chunks from Forge's format to Vanilla's
        Throws:
